# 4. Manual Banner Grabbing

## Objective

Verify Nmap's service detection manually.

## Using Netcat

```bash
nc <TARGET-IP> 80
```

## Using curl

```bash
curl -I http://<TARGET-IP>
```

## Output File

```
raw-output/banner-grab.txt
```

## Explanation

Banner grabbing confirms the actual service running on a port and validates Nmap's version detection.

